{"tid":1142810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】李家超談修例：一般市民根本毋須理會　「我們鴕鳥了22年」須及早堵塞漏洞","createTime":"2019-05-07T10:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T12:25:36.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"2272406fbc4f0232595fd30baa4b9ce6f68d5109","tid":1142810,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190507/s00001/b0b39ce090334cd34b6247c105ad9101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190507%2Fs00001%2Fb0b39ce090334cd34b6247c105ad9101.jpg&h=4448897c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n保安局長李家超下午就《逃犯條例》修訂見記者，被問及立法會議員田北辰提議，可先刪除現行條例中的地域限制，以便先處理台灣殺人案，往後再另交草案處理相關制度漏洞的方案。李家超回應說，「我哋鴕鳥咗22年」，不想再有港人面對台灣殺人案死者家屬情况，要及早堵塞相關漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n李家超回應記者提問時亦提及，「一般市民根本唔需要理會」今次修例，「如果你呢個行為喺香港唔犯法，根本就唔會移交」，包括在港曾出版一些政治書籍、曾發表過一些政治意見、傳媒訪問對政府有一些意見的人等。<br />\n<br />\n他另不點名批評，若指出上述行為或有機會被引渡的人本身有法律背景，「根本係不負責任」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190507/s00001/1557221883236/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190507%2Fs00001%2F1557221883236%2F&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=d3e8abbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190507%2Fs00001%2F1557221883236%2F&h=0edf2d38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190507/s00001/1557221883236/</a>"},{"pid":"206fb4ba23854bf0a36807e5a8861b7cac659644","tid":1142810,"uid":120123,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:19:03.000Z","msg":"屌你食屎啦，依家擺明係信唔過你個政府啦"},{"pid":"ed7784c5bc0a000de9ff944f653a59d6c596b8e6","tid":1142810,"uid":29093,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog